{"tid":1782230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把心愛的支心打碎了","createTime":"2019-12-13T19:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T00:11:05.000Z","uid":79562,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7fa193b2014de41297cb1a9ff9d560dbcf0aba","tid":1782230,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的支心打碎了<br />\n事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞<br />\n發現打碎了的玻璃碎<br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方<br />\n再為其拍照<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/14/ZDqI7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F14%2FZDqI7y.jpg&h=149f72dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uogACj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uogACj.png&h=c9e72713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YHw8Xk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YHw8Xk.png&h=ca1f51c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這短短的三十分鐘<br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間<br />\n打碎了的支心<br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西<br />\n而那玻璃著地的那一聲<br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXPrXQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXPrXQF.png&h=fc5f632d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4vZyoY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4vZyoY.png&h=8ea9ae5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情<br />\n也未必是最糟<br />\n因為最糟的<br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現<br />\n又或者根本就是自己<br />\n我想我找到了答案<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/85/c8/31/85c8315285c9ee432667623780def1de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2F85%2Fc8%2F31%2F85c8315285c9ee432667623780def1de.jpg&h=aee82abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d40b22fcc5bd2744f1468f329f4f2543acec9b9","tid":1782230,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92c2ac56a84529ea2a115bf61f1b40b8d4b33d37","tid":1782230,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2258448ed453c31ec78e3243a11a8f085a61a25f","tid":1782230,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"大文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2958f9122ff3883bdc5e40306d3e64f54ac40b6b","tid":1782230,"uid":141999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T20:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e418754a9b3c7d91a38255d201bac82ec4348da","tid":1782230,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T22:45:55.000Z","msg":"哇睇路成地玻璃"},{"pid":"c4a5113c248a79e2a6246cf24b63377ccaf23049","tid":1782230,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T22:46:44.000Z","msg":"娜娜係乜撚嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d6a5ce11f74dc9fe2712078f9d591cc3b601c6","tid":1782230,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a5113c248a79e2a6246cf24b63377ccaf23049","tid":1782230,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T22:46:44.000Z","msg":"娜娜係乜撚嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T22:56:01.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴喺支那嘅花名"},{"pid":"08ff1d961d38f4539a1dfe32c4c64164eb126717","tid":1782230,"uid":49908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d6a5ce11f74dc9fe2712078f9d591cc3b601c6","tid":1782230,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a5113c248a79e2a6246cf24b63377ccaf23049","tid":1782230,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T22:46:44.000Z","msg":"娜娜係乜撚嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl